prompts.frontCover:
A humorous, flat 2D watercolor painting of a young Asian couple for a birthday card front. The scene features illustrated versions of Lao Lao and Jordan, based on the reference photo. Lao Lao is a young woman with long, straight dark brown hair, wearing thin-framed round glasses, a light blue sweatshirt (without any text or logo), and black pants. She is smiling sweetly and has her arms crossed. Jordan is a young man with short, dark, textured hair, wearing a tan hoodie (without any logos) and dark maroon pants. He stands behind Lao Lao, smiling broadly, with his arms wrapped around her in a loving back hug. The couple is shown from the waist up. Surrounding them are colorful, exaggerated birthday elements like floating confetti, a few whimsical balloons, and a slice of birthday cake with a single lit candle hovering comically near Jordan's hand as if he's offering it. The entire illustration has a soft, flowing watercolor style with visible paper texture, artistic brush strokes, and organic paint bleeds in a bright and cheerful color palette.

In the center of the card, written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday to my favorite person to annoy."

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
